body:
The constructor of SKRect accepts the following parameters:

SKRect(float left, float top, float right, float bottom);

In Extensions.ToSKRect, the following line is used to (incorrectly) convert from Xamarin.Forms.Rectangle to SKRect:
Line 53:
return new SKRect((float)rect.Left, (float)rect.Top, (float)rect.Width, (float)rect.Height);

This line gives width/height values to the resulting rectangle's right and bottom properties.

The fix would look like this:
return new SKRect((float)rect.Left, (float)rect.Top, (float)rect.Right, (float)rect.Bottom);
